title: Episode #35 - Cowhead & ME
description: My buddy & Tampa Bay Radio Personality Mike "Cowhead" Calta and I hang out in the Mancave and talk about him hanging w/ Vince Vaughn, his appearance on Sullivan & Son, Guns in Florida, and trust me when I say the last two minutes are worth it!
